Flicker/Phoenix/Skyblaze::

"Can it, both of you," Flicker orders.  "We gain nothing by fighting 
amongst ourselves."  He looks at Aerotaur.  "Betrayed by your fellow 
Maximals, eh?  That's a new one on me.  We'll see what Hydras thinks 
when he gets out of the CR.  In the meantime, follow me -"  He turns 
and runs right into Phoenix, nearly knocking the smaller bot 
over.  "Oh, sorry," he says, putting out a hand to steady her.  Their 
eyes meet for a moment.

Skyblaze clears his throat, alerting the two lovebirds to the task at 
hand.  Flicker shakes his head and motions for the others to follow 
him inside.
